fields.name: Money Plant ( Small) -  Wood Stand
fields.description:
Cokedama Money Plant ( Small) - with  reclaimed wood stand    

Height with plant approx. 8”, ball diameter approx.4” ,     

Plant type - Goldon pothos-Low maintenance indoor plant.Water: Keep soil moist, but be careful not to overwater.  Pothos do best when their soil is allowed to dry out between waterings Expect to water more often in brighter light and less often in lower light.
